{"tid":511460,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[24小時薯仔Ser] 又到聖誕, 緊係繼續打CS1.6啦~ (2)","createTime":"2017-12-27T13:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T14:30:51.000Z","uid":1402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b5eea3099a7bb03715b711b8f4e6c5508a668116","tid":511460,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cache.www.gametracker.com/server_info/gw1.husky.moe:27018/b_560_95_1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcache.www.gametracker.com%2Fserver_info%2Fgw1.husky.moe%3A27018%2Fb_560_95_1.png&h=f2e19233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果個SER連唔到 有可能轉左IP <br />\n麻煩大家重新ADD多次<br />\n同埋最好就入Telegram睇下有冇最新消息或者尾果幾頁</span></span><br />\n<br />\nIP在此: <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">gw1.husky.moe:27018</span></span><br />\n[入ser方法:開cs1.6&gt;Find Server/尋找伺服器&gt;Favourite/我的最愛&gt;Add Server新增伺服器&gt;copy&amp;paste上面ip ] <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">注意：伺服器只限版本4156(Protocol 48)或以上進入[正盜雙通]</span><br />\n<br />\n如果個我的最愛冇反應(呢個係Non-Steam 4554問題)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請禁 &quot;~&quot;制 &gt;&gt;&gt; 再打connect gw1.husky.moe:27018 &gt;&gt;&gt; enter</span></span><br />\n就入到SER架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTelegram Group: <a href=\"https://husky.moe/telegram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhusky.moe%2Ftelegram&d=uc8ygWNqnQvFNSsWOWl2Cr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=9b5f69de\" target=\"_blank\">https://husky.moe/telegram</a><br />\n(主要用黎召喚D admin上水做野同埋比我同cheesecake發最新公告or更新資訊/比你地召喚下人入SER一齊玩/玩家吹下水咁樣)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Server分為五個模式<br />\n一係普通模式(槍戰/Fun地圖都有)<br />\n二係喪屍模式(以zm_/ze_為前綴既地圖)<br />\n三係搶旗模式(以ctf_為前綴既地圖)<br />\n四係滑水模式(以surf_為前綴既地圖)<br />\n五係雷射捉迷藏(以hns_為前綴既地圖)</span><br />\n玩家可以係Game既控制台打<span style=\"color: red;\">gal_listmaps</span><br />\ncheck下Server有咩地圖，再提名你想玩?地圖<br />\nE.g.: <span style=\"color: red;\">say de_dust2 or say nom de_dust2</span><br />\n姐係提名下張圖係dust2呢張地圖，當RTV夠人就有機會出現係投票List到<br />\n如果你唔想打晒/唔記得完整地圖名既話，可以打 <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">say nom de_</span>，佢會彈一個同de_有關既地圖list比你揀<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">當然，提名地圖都有D限制，當目前地圖係ZM/ZE時，你唔可以提名下張圖係ZM/ZE map，即使提名左都唔會出現投票list到。<br />\n另外，部分地圖設有時段限制，呢D地圖只會係某個時段先可以提名同玩到。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你DOWN MAP慢既話 請重新開過隻GAME 咁樣會快返...<br />\n呢個係因為Client side bug既關係 令到你冇連去網空DOWN野<br />\n除非Valve出更新fix返 不過2017既CS更新都係冇fix到個bug <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打/msg xxxxxx可以自訂稱號<br />\neg /msg I Love Husky<br />\n咁我講野就會顯示<br />\n[<span style=\"color: blue;\">I Love Husky</span>]<span style=\"color: orange;\">Husky</span>: 仲唔快D入黎玩<br />\n(2017 CS更新整到bug左, 得閒先fix)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果你發現玩家用D不正當程式/腳本/漏洞進行遊戲，請用Admin Chat通知在線admin(say_team+@) 或者 係Telegram Group通知admin處理。</span></span>"},{"pid":"c4ae8f7fe7953edc995737619f5e5f7e1f51b013","tid":511460,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"CS Download Link: <a href=\"https://lmgtfy.com/?q=warzone+cs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flmgtfy.com%2F%3Fq%3Dwarzone%2Bcs&d=uc8ygWNqnQvFNSsWOWl2Cr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a81efd84\" target=\"_blank\">https://lmgtfy.com/?q=warzone+cs</a> <br />\n第一個結果就有download link <br />\n入面篇有個Direct Download 隔離就係DOWNLOAD LINK啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nHKG CS1.6 By Husky(Non-Steam 4554) Final <br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B28asyuYbDU0LXpQMDVDdkhFR1k/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0B28asyuYbDU0LXpQMDVDdkhFR1k%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=uc8ygWNqnQvFNSsWOWl2Cr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=966c36b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B28asyuYbDU0LXpQMDVDdkhFR1k/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n內置埋中文輸入 唔使再用csmate先打到中文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n亦都可以買正版支持下呢隻GAME<br />\n其實都唔係好貴 當支持下班開發者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/10/CounterStrike/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F10%2FCounterStrike%2F&d=uc8ygWNqnQvFNSsWOWl2Cr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=7e1062b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/10/CounterStrike/</a> <br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n伺服器即時戰況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lgsl.husky.moe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flgsl.husky.moe%2F&d=uc8ygWNqnQvFNSsWOWl2Cr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=e6199cb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://lgsl.husky.moe/</a><br />\nAddons:<br />\nSteam CS玩家可以利用此CS1.6伺服器列表開啟Steam CS並進入伺服器 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n開唔到GAME問題(Windows 8用/Windows 10自行測試): <br />\n<a href=\"https://windows.microsoft.com/zh-hk/windows7/Change-Data-Execution-Prevention-settings?SignedIn=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwindows.microsoft.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fwindows7%2FChange-Data-Execution-Prevention-settings%3FSignedIn%3D1&d=uc8ygWNqnQvFNSsWOWl2Cr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=91e5b567\" target=\"_blank\">https://windows.microsoft.com/zh-hk/windows7/Change-Data-Execution-Prevention-settings?SignedIn=1</a> <br />\n加番個cstrike.exe入去DEP LIST就可以開到GAME啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456b560c0b02b98a8988ba1a268bc6a316f332c0",