"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"today 2359+-15mins off ser that's all <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6561bfcc61024f6954c948a951b19ff06fd430aa","tid":511460,"uid":1402,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"tldr version<br />\n呢個SER過埋今日就唔會再開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的...<br />\n呢個Ser過埋今日就會正式停止服務<br />\n唔經唔覺, 呢個SER都開咗差唔多三年<br />\n由初期喪屍Ser發展到去槍ser<br />\n上年更加由兩個SER合併埋一齊<br />\n係玩家嘅提議下，再加多咗幾個模式<br />\n最近，更加多咗個hns模式比大家玩下<br />\n變到依家咁，有5個模式選擇<br />\n大家都可以揀玩唔同嘅野<br />\n<br />\n可惜嘅係，CS1.6敵唔過時間呢樣野<br />\n呢幾年愈黎愈少人玩，好多人都轉晒去其他game<br />\n亦可能大家都大過啦，唔會再有D咩時間去打機<br />\n有D做緊野，有D入咗U/HD/ASSO，大家都好忙<br />\n同時，我地亦因為咁樣都少咗更新個喪屍mode<br />\n<br />\n呢個Server兩年嘅人數<br />\n最初長期32/32跌到去依家嘅長期0/32<br />\n由初初嘅5點就開始多人玩<br />\n上年去到7點先開始多人玩<br />\n甚至今年暑假，去到9點先會多人玩<br />\n直到呢個聖誕，有玩嘅都有目共睹<br />\n長期都冇咩人玩 0/32<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地經過討論後<br />\n都一致決定開埋今次假期就結束所有服務<br />\n<br />\n多謝晒大家一直以黎嘅支持<br />\n另外，亦都多謝咁多位admin<br />\nwa!gor,star,nok,baines,colcol<br />\n<br />\n祝各位新一年順順利利<br />\n<br />\n有緣再聚<br />\n<br />\nHusky, CheeseCake"},{"pid":"ab85e4381d04cdc9c1da29d5bd50ab11319ef4db","tid":511460,"uid":5313,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:35:19.000Z","msg":"感受大家一直支持。<br />\n係度我都有少少野想講。喪屍插件(Contagion X)係我由2014年岩岩DSE完開始寫，當中經過無數dup code同test既日子，試過遇到好多BUG，又有當時好難解決既問題，但最後都一一解決。到左依家，呢個成為第一個我叫佢'Stable' 既插件。過程好辛苦，整既時間絕對唔比我玩既時間少，但係見到一眾玩家玩得咁開心，我內心真係覺得好滿足，我諗呢個就係寫game既樂趣，因此我唔覺得付出既時間係白費。<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝Core當日係論壇邀請我一齊搞呢個server，比左一個平台Contagion X為大家服務，如果唔係呢個插件冇可能run到咁多年，當中佢都幫呢個插件改左唔少Bug同做optimization，成個SER佢付出係最最最大。<br />\n<br />\n最後再一次多謝大家支持連登高登CS1.6 Server，有緣再聚。<br />\n<br />\nContagion X 作者<br />\nCheese Cake"},{"pid":"7a23482aa9defe7008fd365d8b483032f90ca16a","tid":511460,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T16:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ac74bb6f603d00eae34570a3a10ad08dc4ed21","tid":511460,"uid":21761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372ea95eb77ac908e73abd4c8cde1e2ad9859424","tid":511460,"uid":37665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"我愛大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e51ce45bd6742f44e66a3e425f3fe0ea02d6dc","tid":511460,"uid":8976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:04:51.000Z","msg":"無人可以執左個SER<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8670fbfa2d11a5d24029caf08e062ebe41aba67","tid":511460,"uid":37665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:11:26.000Z","msg":"叮噹可否不要老<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65430b7a5993d7887d6594c79284f8c5044a067","tid":511460,"uid":8976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8670fbfa2d11a5d24029caf08e062ebe41aba67","tid":511460,"uid":37665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:11:26.000Z","msg":"叮噹可否不要老<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"伴我到老<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e32d810a3885445239f322c3507994ce039c306","tid":511460,"uid":3558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:58:50.000Z","msg":"今日先睇到哩個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n